07:30:49.799 --> 07:30:51.479
Hi, this is Tooey Sutherland.

07:30:51.540 --> 07:30:54.599
A Nightwing Guide to the Dragons of

07:30:54.599 --> 07:30:55.200
Pyrea.

07:30:55.259 --> 07:30:57.419
Sand wings.

07:30:57.479 --> 07:30:58.979
Description.

07:30:59.040 --> 07:31:01.680
Pale gold or white scales, the color of

07:31:01.680 --> 07:31:05.639
desert sand, poisonous barbed tail, forked

07:31:05.639 --> 07:31:06.299
black tongues.

07:31:06.419 --> 07:31:10.380
Abilities can survive a long time without

07:31:10.380 --> 07:31:10.799
water.

07:31:10.799 --> 07:31:13.139
Poison enemies with the tips of their

07:31:13.139 --> 07:31:14.279
tails like scorpions.

07:31:14.340 --> 07:31:16.740
Bury themselves for camouflage in the

07:31:16.740 --> 07:31:17.340
desert sand.

07:31:17.400 --> 07:31:18.720
Breathe fire.

07:31:18.779 --> 07:31:20.939
Queen.

07:31:21.000 --> 07:31:23.880
Since the death of Queen Oasis, the tribe

07:31:23.880 --> 07:31:26.099
is split between 3 rivals for the throne

07:31:26.099 --> 07:31:28.979
sisters burn, blister, and blaze.

07:31:29.099 --> 07:31:31.560
Alliances.

07:31:31.619 --> 07:31:34.680
Byrne fights alongside Skywings and

07:31:34.680 --> 07:31:35.340
Mudwings.

07:31:35.459 --> 07:31:38.700
Blister is allied with the sea wings, and

07:31:38.700 --> 07:31:41.099
Blaze has the support of most sand wings

07:31:41.099 --> 07:31:42.779
as well as an alliance with the ice

07:31:42.779 --> 07:31:43.080
wings.

07:31:43.139 --> 07:31:45.599
Mudwings.

07:31:45.659 --> 07:31:49.740
Description, thick armored brown scales

07:31:49.740 --> 07:31:51.060
sometimes with amber and gold

07:31:51.060 --> 07:31:51.779
underscales.

07:31:51.840 --> 07:31:54.779
Large flat heads with nostrils on top of

07:31:54.779 --> 07:31:55.139
the snout.

07:31:55.259 --> 07:31:58.919
Abilities, can breathe fire if warm

07:31:58.919 --> 07:31:59.220
enough.

07:31:59.279 --> 07:32:02.520
Hold their breath for up to an hour, blend

07:32:02.520 --> 07:32:04.799
into large mud puddles, usually very

07:32:04.799 --> 07:32:05.099
strong.

07:32:05.159 --> 07:32:08.400
Queen, queen moorhen.

07:32:08.459 --> 07:32:12.299
Alliances, currently allied with Burn and

07:32:12.299 --> 07:32:13.680
the Sky Wings in the Great War.

07:32:13.799 --> 07:32:16.500
Sky Wings.

07:32:16.560 --> 07:32:20.099
Description, red gold or orange scales

07:32:20.099 --> 07:32:21.240
enormous wings.

07:32:21.360 --> 07:32:25.380
Abilities, powerful fighters and fliers

07:32:25.380 --> 07:32:26.459
can breathe fire.

07:32:26.520 --> 07:32:29.459
Queen, Queen Scarlet.

07:32:29.520 --> 07:32:33.479
Alliances, currently allied with Burn and

07:32:33.479 --> 07:32:34.680
the Mudwings in the Great War.

07:32:34.740 --> 07:32:37.500
Sea Wings.

07:32:37.560 --> 07:32:41.220
Description, blue or green or aquamarine

07:32:41.220 --> 07:32:44.639
scales, webs between their claws, gills

07:32:44.639 --> 07:32:46.979
on their necks, glow in the dark stripes

07:32:46.979 --> 07:32:48.779
on their tails, snouts, underbellies.

07:32:48.840 --> 07:32:53.099
Abilities, can breathe underwater, see in

07:32:53.099 --> 07:32:55.500
the dark, create huge waves with one

07:32:55.500 --> 07:32:56.819
splash of their powerful tails.

07:32:56.880 --> 07:32:58.560
Excellent swimmers.

07:32:58.680 --> 07:33:01.799
Queen, Queen Coral.

07:33:01.860 --> 07:33:05.759
Alliances, currently allied with blister

07:33:05.759 --> 07:33:06.540
in the Great War.

07:33:06.659 --> 07:33:09.240
Ice Wings.

07:33:09.360 --> 07:33:12.659
Description, silvery scales like the moon

07:33:12.659 --> 07:33:13.919
or pale blue like ice.

07:33:13.979 --> 07:33:18.000
Ridged claws to grip the ice, forked blue

07:33:18.000 --> 07:33:20.520
tongues, tails narrow to a whip thin

07:33:20.520 --> 07:33:20.759
end.

07:33:20.819 --> 07:33:24.720
Abilities can withstand subzero

07:33:24.720 --> 07:33:26.220
temperatures and bright light.

07:33:26.220 --> 07:33:28.319
Exhale a deadly, freezing breath.

07:33:28.380 --> 07:33:31.560
Queen, Queen Glacier.

07:33:31.560 --> 07:33:33.479
Alliances.

07:33:33.479 --> 07:33:36.119
Currently allied with Blaze and most of

07:33:36.119 --> 07:33:37.500
the sandwings in the Great War.

07:33:37.560 --> 07:33:40.080
Rain wings.

07:33:40.139 --> 07:33:41.759
Description.

07:33:41.819 --> 07:33:44.099
Scales constantly shift colors, usually

07:33:44.099 --> 07:33:46.979
bright like birds of paradise, prehensile

07:33:46.979 --> 07:33:47.340
tales.

07:33:47.400 --> 07:33:51.599
Abilities, can camouflage their scales to

07:33:51.599 --> 07:33:52.740
blend into their surroundings.

07:33:52.799 --> 07:33:55.380
Use their prehensile tails for climbing

07:33:55.380 --> 07:33:57.540
no known natural weapons.

07:33:57.599 --> 07:34:00.720
Queen, Queen dazzling.

07:34:00.779 --> 07:34:04.560
Alliances, not involved in the Great

07:34:04.560 --> 07:34:04.919
War.

07:34:04.979 --> 07:34:07.380
Nightwings.

07:34:07.439 --> 07:34:11.099
Description, purplish black scales and

07:34:11.099 --> 07:34:13.020
scattered silver scales on the underside

07:34:13.020 --> 07:34:15.000
of their wings, like a night sky full of

07:34:15.000 --> 07:34:15.299
stars.

07:34:15.419 --> 07:34:17.400
Forked black tongues.

07:34:17.459 --> 07:34:21.840
Abilities, can breathe fire, disappear

07:34:21.840 --> 07:34:25.139
into dark shadows, read minds, foretell

07:34:25.139 --> 07:34:25.500
the future.

07:34:25.619 --> 07:34:29.279
Queen, a closely guarded secret.

07:34:29.340 --> 07:34:33.659
Alliances, too mysterious and powerful to

07:34:33.659 --> 07:34:34.439
be part of the war.
